economy, which is

00:12:14.810 --> 00:12:18.720 align:middle line:84%
working itself toward
the self destruction

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:19.970 align:middle line:90%
of the financial system.

00:12:19.970 --> 00:12:22.910 align:middle line:84%
