00:12:42.930 --> 00:12:44.350 align:middle line:84%
for the emergence
of a new world.

00:12:44.350 --> 00:12:47.280 align:middle line:84%
And that's what I spend my
time trying to think about,

00:12:47.280 --> 00:12:50.120 align:middle line:84%
is what's this new world,
and what might it look like,

00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:51.290 align:middle line:90%
and how might it work?

00:12:51.290 --> 00:12:53.820 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it seemed leading
up to, for instance, 2012,

00:12:53.820 --> 00:12:57.160 align:middle line:84%
it seemed more likely that
this-- this disruptive event

00:12:57.160 --> 00:13:00.260 align:middle line:84%
on the financial scale
or whatever might happen

00:13:00.260 --> 00:13:01.730 align:middle line:90%
more rapidly or radically.

00:13:01.730 --> 00:13:04.050 align:middle line:84%
And in a sense, I think some
people, myself included,

00:13:04.050 --> 00:13:07.090 align:middle line:84%
are actually kind of impressed
with how the system has

00:13:07.090 --> 00:13:08.570 align:middle line:84%
