00:14:41.094 --> 00:14:42.060 align:middle line:90%
than in any time in the past.

00:14:42.060 --> 00:14:43.660 align:middle line:84%
So you don't, for instance,
agree with somebody

00:14:43.660 --> 00:14:44.790 align:middle line:84%
