00:17:21.329 --> 00:17:24.230 align:middle line:84%
But if you have a human
being, like a research--

00:17:24.230 --> 00:17:26.050 align:middle line:84%
like a research
assistant or someone

00:17:26.050 --> 00:17:29.030 align:middle line:84%
like that, that goes
out to find things,

00:17:29.030 --> 00:17:31.970 align:middle line:84%
and checks with somebody
else, and makes decisions,

00:17:31.970 --> 00:17:33.270 align:middle line:90%
and comes back, and so on.

00:17:33.270 --> 00:17:36.040 align:middle line:84%
I'd-- I tell the story about--
