00:17:36.040 --> 00:17:37.760 align:middle line:90%
I need some tires on my car.

00:17:37.760 --> 00:17:39.330 align:middle line:90%
And the agent says, well, OK.

00:17:39.330 --> 00:17:40.840 align:middle line:84%
And the agent knows
what kind of car

00:17:40.840 --> 00:17:42.900 align:middle line:84%
you got, and knows
what size tires,

00:17:42.900 --> 00:17:44.140 align:middle line:84%
and knows how long
you've driven it,

00:17:44.140 --> 00:17:45.440 align:middle line:84%
and it goes, and
finds them, and says--

00:17:45.440 --> 00:17:46.720 align:middle line:84%
So-- so in that
sense, you're seeing

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:50.130 align:middle line:84%
a world where technology
is more responsive

00:17:50.130 --> 00:17:53.490 align:middle line:90%
