00:19:01.280 --> 00:19:03.170 align:middle line:90%
multiple cellular life, right?

00:19:03.170 --> 00:19:05.620 align:middle line:84%
And so we are
literally at this place

00:19:05.620 --> 00:19:10.630 align:middle line:84%
where the future is, in
general terms, unthinkable.

00:19:10.630 --> 00:19:13.850 align:middle line:84%
It has the potential to be
so dramatically different

00:19:13.850 --> 00:19:14.870 align:middle line:90%
than anything we think.

00:19:14.870 --> 00:19:18.930 align:middle line:84%
So if you buy that and you're
able to kind of work your way

00:19:18.930 --> 00:19:21.300 align:middle line:84%
into that space to make some
sense out of it, what you

00:19:21.300 --> 00:19:23.080 align:middle line:84%
immediately do is
start to say, well,

00:19:23.080 --> 00:19:24.890 align:middle line:90%
what could we do differently?

00:19:24.890 --> 00:19:26.780 align:middle line:84%
And you end at the
psychic and the-- the--

00:19:26.780 --> 00:19:30.220 align:middle line:84%
and the ability to
do-- do-- do telepathy,

00:19:30.220 --> 00:19:33.470 align:middle line:84%
and to manifestation, and any
number of other kind of things.

00:19:33.470 --> 00:19:35.890 align:middle line:90%
And the indicators are there.

00:19:35.890 --> 00:19:38.001 align:middle line:90%
And there are many kind of--

00:19:38.001 --> 00:19:39.700 align:middle line:84%
What-- what do you mean,
the indicators are there?

00:19:39.700 --> 00:19:42.390 align:middle line:84%
I mean, there's
many, many sources,

00:19:42.390 --> 00:19:45.690 align:middle line:84%
necessarily unconventional
because this is-- we're talking

00:19:45.690 --> 00:19:49.590 align:middle line:84%
unconventional things, who
independently come to the--

