conclusion and say, well,

00:19:52.180 --> 00:19:54.310 align:middle line:84%
one of the characteristics
of this in the human

00:19:54.310 --> 00:19:57.150 align:middle line:84%
is going to be the ability
to manifest faster.

00:19:57.150 --> 00:20:00.900 align:middle line:84%
Right now, the best
guess and understanding

00:20:00.900 --> 00:20:03.510 align:middle line:84%
