works is consciousness

00:20:03.510 --> 00:20:04.280 align:middle line:90%
is causal.

00:20:04.280 --> 00:20:07.730 align:middle line:84%
And your consciousness in
time kind of manifests itself

00:20:07.730 --> 00:20:08.880 align:middle line:90%
