people being able to manifest

00:20:38.666 --> 00:20:41.510 align:middle line:84%
and-- and produce
the essential kind

00:20:41.510 --> 00:20:44.761 align:middle line:84%
of functions and components
of the new world.

00:20:44.761 --> 00:20:45.460 align:middle line:90%
Cool.

