So what I get from you is
that all we've got to do

00:20:47.126 --> 00:20:50.630 align:middle line:84%
is think the unthinkable and
accelerate the manifestation.

00:20:50.630 --> 00:20:53.510 align:middle line:84%
It-- it-- it's not
quite that simple,

00:20:53.510 --> 00:20:54.876 align:middle line:84%
but that's essentially it.
Yeah.

00:20:54.876 --> 00:20:55.840 align:middle line:84%
-Right on.
