00:21:35.070 --> 00:21:35.770 align:middle line:90%
And yeah.

00:21:35.770 --> 00:21:37.310 align:middle line:90%
And you kind of shape it.

00:21:37.310 --> 00:21:39.660 align:middle line:84%
But that's what
does not exist now.

00:21:39.660 --> 00:21:42.800 align:middle line:84%
A model of what the new world
looks like does not exist.

00:21:42.800 --> 00:21:45.210 align:middle line:84%
And that's what one of the
projects that we're working on

00:21:45.210 --> 00:21:47.600 align:middle line:84%
