-Thanks.

00:22:55.189 --> 00:22:56.970 align:middle line:84%
And so tell me a
little bit about Artsy.

00:22:56.970 --> 00:22:59.950 align:middle line:10%
How you got started with
it and what your vision is.

00:22:59.950 --> 00:23:00.970 align:middle line:90%
Sure.

00:23:00.970 --> 00:23:04.540 align:middle line:84%
So at Artsy, our
vision is we want art

00:23:04.540 --> 00:23:07.500 align:middle line:84%
to become as important
a part of human culture

00:23:07.500 --> 00:23:10.220 align:middle line:90%
as music is today.

00:23:10.220 --> 00:23:12.310 align:middle line:84%
Our mission is to
make all the world's

00:23:12.310 --> 00:23:14.630 align:middle line:84%
art accessible to anyone
with an internet connection.

00:23:14.630 --> 00:23:17.880 align:middle line:84%
That's how we think we're going
to make our vision possible.

00:23:17.880 --> 00:23:21.330 align:middle line:10%
And our goal, as a business--
so we are-- we're a for-profit.

00:23:21.330 --> 00:23:24.460 align:middle line:10%
And the only way
something so ambitious

00:23:24.460 --> 00:23:27.060 align:middle line:10%
would ever be
financially possible

00:23:27.060 --> 00:23:30.350 align:middle line:10%
or sustainable is by
tapping into the market

00:23:30.350 --> 00:23:31.960 align:middle line:10%
and also expanding
the art market.

00:23:31.960 --> 00:23:34.690 align:middle line:84%
So as a business, our goal,
certainly in the short term,

00:23:34.690 --> 00:23:38.130 align:middle line:84%
is to be the best place on
the internet to discover art,

00:23:38.130 --> 00:23:41.450 align:middle line:84%
and also to collect
art, and buy art.

00:23:41.450 --> 00:23:45.660 align:middle line:84%
On Artsy, we have, by
far, the largest rights

00:23:45.660 --> 00:23:49.300 align:middle line:84%
cleared database of modern
and contemporary fine art

00:23:49.300 --> 00:23:51.150 align:middle line:90%
in the world.

00:23:51.150 --> 00:23:53.310 align:middle line:84%
You can go there and you
can learn all about it.

00:23:53.310 --> 00:23:55.900 align:middle line:84%
We also have something called
The Art Genome Project, which

00:23:55.900 --> 00:23:59.850 align:middle line:84%
is inspired by Pandora's
Music Genome Project, which

00:23:59.850 --> 00:24:01.740 align:middle line:84%
is essentially
metadata that's applied

00:24:01.740 --> 00:24:03.330 align:middle line:90%
to every artist and artwork.

00:24:03.330 --> 00:24:05.480 align:middle line:84%
We call this metadata--
we call them genes.

00:24:05.480 --> 00:24:07.930 align:middle line:84%
But what they really
are is they are

00:24:07.930 --> 00:24:11.810 align:middle line:84%
scores for every
possible characteristic

00:24:11.810 --> 00:24:12.770 align:middle line:90%
that could apply to art.

00:24:12.770 --> 00:24:15.300 align:middle line:84%
So for instance, you could
imagine a Mark Rothko work

00:24:15.300 --> 00:24:18.040 align:middle line:84%
having 100 in abstract
expressionism,

00:24:18.040 --> 00:24:22.080 align:middle line:84%
and 100 in New York school,
and maybe an 80 in color field

00:24:22.080 --> 00:24:27.120 align:middle line:84%
painting, and maybe a 40 in
geometric because of the sort

00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:29.890 align:middle line:90%
of rough geometric composition.

00:24:29.890 --> 00:24:32.730 align:middle line:84%
And the average artwork
has between 20 to 30 genes.

00:24:32.730 --> 00:24:35.930 align:middle line:84%
We use The Art Genome Project
to recommend other works of art

00:24:35.930 --> 00:24:36.980 align:middle line:90%
you might like.

00:24:36.980 --> 00:24:39.365 align:middle line:84%
And so people can sort
of trace paths through--

00:24:39.365 --> 00:24:40.665 align:middle line:84%
So in the same way,
if I go to Amazon,

00:24:40.665 --> 00:24:42.220 align:middle line:90%
it will recommend books to me.

00:24:42.220 --> 00:24:46.100 align:middle line:84%
Or if I go to Spotify,
it'll recommend music.

00:24:46.100 --> 00:24:47.670 align:middle line:84%
And so on.
-Yeah, exactly.

00:24:47.670 --> 00:24:49.540 align:middle line:84%
And so it's a way to
both learn about the art,

00:24:49.540 --> 00:24:52.960 align:middle line:84%
but also discover new things
and kind of walk through space

00:24:52.960 --> 00:24:55.200 align:middle line:90%
and time through art history.

00:24:55.200 --> 00:24:56.760 align:middle line:84%
And if you're
interested in buying,

00:24:56.760 --> 00:24:58.110 align:middle line:84%
you can also see
what's exhibiting

00:24:58.110 --> 00:25:00.270 align:middle line:84%
at all the top galleries
around the world.

