00:25:09.130 --> 00:25:10.530 align:middle line:84%
I mean, was there--
did you come into this

00:25:10.530 --> 00:25:12.770 align:middle line:84%
with some particular
mission or sense

00:25:12.770 --> 00:25:15.355 align:middle line:84%
that there was like a need
that needed to be met here?

00:25:15.355 --> 00:25:16.350 align:middle line:90%
You know, it's interesting.

00:25:16.350 --> 00:25:18.990 align:middle line:84%
Like I don't have the typical
background of an entrepreneur.

00:25:18.990 --> 00:25:23.010 align:middle line:84%
I was not selling
lemonade as a kid,

00:25:23.010 --> 00:25:25.011 align:middle line:84%
