00:25:27.180 --> 00:25:29.430 align:middle line:84%
And from a very young
age, I was extremely lucky

00:25:29.430 --> 00:25:32.930 align:middle line:84%
that I got-- well, often
dragged to galleries

00:25:32.930 --> 00:25:34.250 align:middle line:90%
and museums as a kid.

00:25:34.250 --> 00:25:36.930 align:middle line:84%
And he would, very patiently,
talk to me about the art.

00:25:36.930 --> 00:25:40.830 align:middle line:84%
And so I had this very kind
of strong passion for art

00:25:40.830 --> 00:25:41.600 align:middle line:90%
from a young age.

00:25:41.600 --> 00:25:43.930 align:middle line:84%
But actually, my
mom's side of family

00:25:43.930 --> 00:25:47.300 align:middle line:84%
