00:25:48.100 --> 00:25:52.400 align:middle line:84%
And what I really excelled at,
as a kid, was math and physics.

00:25:52.400 --> 00:25:55.541 align:middle line:84%
And my goal was actually to
be a theoretical physicist

00:25:55.541 --> 00:25:56.240 align:middle line:90%
when I grew up.

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:58.730 align:middle line:84%
So I originally went
to school for physics,

00:25:58.730 --> 00:26:01.850 align:middle line:84%
