in love with programming.

00:26:01.850 --> 00:26:04.440 align:middle line:84%
And particularly, I saw a course
called Artificial Intelligence.

00:26:04.440 --> 00:26:06.900 align:middle line:84%
And I guess I read a lot of
science fiction as a kid.

00:26:06.900 --> 00:26:08.900 align:middle line:84%
And so when I-- when I saw
that I could actually now

00:26:08.900 --> 00:26:11.190 align:middle line:84%
