00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:17.010 align:middle line:90%
And I fell in love programming.

00:26:17.010 --> 00:26:18.590 align:middle line:84%
And it was during my
senior year of college

00:26:18.590 --> 00:26:20.570 align:middle line:84%
